(59306, 169633, 0, 1, 'Your Redemption', '中文翻譯:\r\n\r\n我獨自佇立在滂沱大雨之中\r\n希望這場雨能洗靜我身上的罪\r\n救救我吧! 請抹去我的傷痛\r\n我需要找到一個屬於我的地方\r\n\r\n我為了你們的懺悔而唱\r\n我為了你們的解放而戰\r\n請你們注意這裡\r\n因為我便是救贖之道\r\n別再叫我忍耐\r\n我已經站在這裡了\r\n現在跟我一起衝破這道牆吧!\r\n你還在等什麼呢?\r\n\r\n偏執狂的個性正在呼喚著我\r\n日復一日 我的感覺仍一如往常\r\n救救我吧! 請抹去我的傷痛\r\n我需要找到一個屬於我的地方\r\n\r\n我為了你們的懺悔而唱\r\n我為了你們的解放而戰\r\n請你們注意這裡\r\n因為我便是救贖之道\r\n別再叫我忍耐\r\n我已經站在這裡了\r\n現在跟我一起衝破這道牆吧!\r\n你還在等什麼呢?\r\n\r\n你等夠了沒有?!\r\n\r\n破壞吧!!\r\n他們推我上台並給了我權位\r\n接著玩死我還砸了我的皇冠\r\n你們弄我 我根本不在乎\r\n因為我可不是你們的小木偶\r\n誰都無法再阻止我! 誰都不行!\r\n\r\n我為了你們的懺悔而唱\r\n我為了你們的解放而戰\r\n請你們注意這裡\r\n因為我便是救贖之道\r\n別再叫我忍耐\r\n我已經站在這裡了\r\n現在跟我一起衝破這道牆吧!\r\n你還在等什麼呢?\r\n你還站在這幹嘛?', '2013-01-18 00:00:00', 2012, 0, 1, 7, 'I stand alone in this heavy rain.\r\nAnd hope these drops are gonna wash my sins away.\r\nSo help me out, please erase my wreck.\r\nI try to find the place. (that belongs to me)\r\n\r\nI sing for confession, I fight for liberation.\r\nMay I have your attention.\r\nCuz I''m your redemption.\r\nDon''t tell me to be patient, cuz I''m already here.\r\nNow just crush the wall.\r\nSo what are you waiting for?\r\n\r\nMy paranoid is calling out my name.\r\nDay after day, what I feel is still the same.\r\nSo help me out, please erase my wreck.\r\nI try to find the place. (that belongs to me)\r\n\r\nI sing for confession, I fight for liberation.\r\nMay I have your attention.\r\nCuz I''m your redemption.\r\n\r\nDon''t tell me to be patient, cuz I''m already here.\r\nNow just crush the wall.\r\nSo what are you waiting for?\r\n\r\nSo what are you waiting for?\r\n\r\nBreak it down!!\r\nThey push me up, and gave me throne.\r\nThey fuck me up, then smash my crown.\r\nYou set me up? I don''t give a fuck.\r\nCuz I am not your Pinocchio.\r\nNothing can stop us anymore!\r\nNot anymore!\r\n\r\nI sing for confession, I fight for liberation.\r\nMay I have your attention.\r\nCuz I''m your redemption.\r\n\r\nDon''t tell me to be patient, cuz I''m already here.\r\nNow just crush the wall.\r\nSo why are you stand still?', '', 188